#
# ROOM LAYOUT:
#   Reception → Main Office Area (KEY) → Multiple rooms branch:
#     - Storage Closet (unlocked, Derek's safe)
#     - Break Room (unlocked, clues)
#     - Conference Room (unlocked, evidence)
#     - IT Room (PIN 2468, Kevin + lockpicks + keycard)
